Use the standard library
This is how to triples_sum_to_zero of l:
  Remember that count is 0
  Remember that n is l's length
  Do this n times:
    Decrease n
    Remember that a is item n in l
    Remember that m is n
    Do this m times:
      Decrease m
      Remember that b is item m in l
      Remember that k is m
      Do this k times:
        Decrease k
        Remember that c is item k in l
        When sum of a and b and c is 0, then:
          Increase count
        End when
      End do
    End do
  End do
  The answer is count
Now you know